Step 1:Install apk in android phone.- clicking on it will install

 

Step 2: Buttons : Enable Overlay Permission,

Step 3. Enable Accessibility Service

 

click both button and give permission to SampleApp to overlay so that it shows you the time transparently

step 4   select SampleApp - ON after clicking "Enable Overlay Permission"

 

 

Step 5:  select SampleApp  after clicking "Enable Accessibility Service" button

 

and select ON

 

 

minimise the app and scroll or use other apps and scroll to see the time in teh center of the screen and number of scrolls warnings.

 

The app gives a maximum of 7 minutes to spend. If you close the app, the screen warnings and timer will vanish.

 

it gives warnings for a second - like this " 50 scrolls" ,,.. after some more scrolls "100 scrolls" etc..
